00:00:12,450 --> 00:00:15,963
First, we need to add a dropdown right here.

6
00:00:16,980 --> 00:00:20,100
Before we even add that dropdown, we need a list

7
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:24,033
of all the categories that we can display in the dropdown.

8
00:00:25,020 --> 00:00:28,440
So first, we need to retrieve that in the controller.

9
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,900
If I open the product controller,

